{"TopicId":62670,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[Patch][0.23] NOTAM-IVA-Altimeter - fix your IVA Altimeter","CreatedByName":"Tabakhase","CreatedById":101288,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T17:12:37Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tabakhase","CreatedById":101288,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T17:12:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ENOTAM-IVA-Altimeter\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E for KSP \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003E0.23\u003C/span\u003E - \u003Cem\u003Ereleased 2014-02-09\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EReassigns the \u003Cstrong\u003EIVA-Altimeter-Hands\u003C/strong\u003E (InternalAltimeterThreeHands) to use \u0027Notice to Airmen\u0027 readings - means:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003Ehand100Name = MediumArm\u003Cbr\u003Ehand1000Name = ShortArm\u003Cbr\u003Ehand10000Name = LongArm\u003C/pre\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Einstead off\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003Ehand100Name = LongArm\u003Cbr\u003Ehand1000Name = MediumArm\u003Cbr\u003Ehand10000Name = ShortArm\u003C/pre\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003EDownload\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbal.curseforge.com/ksp-mods/222254-notam-iva-altimeter\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E@CurseForge\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAll credit on the \u0022what to change\u0022 goes to \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.reddit.com/user/deckard58\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ereddit/u/deckard58\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIm forming this into a \u0022downloadable addon\u0022 on request - dont even ask me if that is correct or not ;P\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERequires\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/55219\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EModuleManager\u003C/a\u003E \u0026gt;= 1.5.5\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELicense\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- Released as public domain.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E- Source: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.reddit.com/r/KerbalSpaceProgram/comments/1jnkas/notam_how_to_fix_the_iva_altimeter/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.reddit.com/r/KerbalSpaceProgram/comments/1jnkas/notam_how_to_fix_the_iva_altimeter/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECredits what to change: reddit/u/deckard58 \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWrapped in ModuleManager-Syntax: Tabakhase\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/wt2W3\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EJavascript is disabled. View full album\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-07-10T10:44:34Z\u0022 title=\u002207/10/2014 10:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 10, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Tabakhase\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Euploaded to CurseForge\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-31T12:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s disappointing that this this simple but excellent mod gets so little attention. It\u0027s such a simple fix. Needs to be stock.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-24T09:23:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFast approaching two years later, I am forced to conclude that the number of KSP players who care about the correctness of the IVA altimeter\u00A0 -\u00A0 or indeed even \u003Cem\u003Enotice\u003C/em\u003E the issue\u00A0 -\u00A0 is so vanishingly small as to be insignificant.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"White Owl","CreatedById":10849,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-06T13:48:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a tradition now. Once a year, I\u0027ll bring this thread back up just to let any interested parties know about the simple and elegant fix to one of KSP\u0027s longest-running bugs. A bug so very persistent that the fraction of the userbase who ever attempt to use the IVA altimeter just train themselves to read it the \u003Cem\u003Ewrong damn way\u003C/em\u003E instead of seeking a fix.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nightside","CreatedById":150244,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-06T19:50:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/101288-tabakhase/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022101288\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/101288-tabakhase/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Tabakhase\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u0026amp;\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10849-white-owl/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002210849\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/10849-white-owl/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@White Owl\u003C/a\u003E, it looks like the DL link is broken. This patch should work if anyone is interested.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@PROP[AltimeterThreeHands]\u003Cbr\u003E\n{\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 @MODULE[InternalAltimeterThreeHands]\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 {\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 @hand100Name = MediumArm\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 @hand1000Name = ShortArm\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 @hand10000Name = LongArm\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 }\u003Cbr\u003E\n}\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"splintermuffins","CreatedById":227797,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-14T14:42:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is 2023, they are dropping KSP2. This fix is still not stock and this should be fixed in the base game. IMHO.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}